The Infinity Group has said it will not compromise quality in order to give vehicle owners the durability they desire in their vehicles. Infinity Tyres Director Vineet Mathur stated this during a briefing to unveil the 2018 Value drive offer to give back to the customers. Value drive which is in its 16th edition is a platform created by the group to give customers a ahance to experience quality automotive aftermarket products and win gifts nationwide. The offer is part of the company’s efforts to appreciate customers’ patronage yearly.